high.mackenzie.autumn.lang.compiler.typesystem

Class ReflectiveDeclaredType

  • java.lang.Object
    • high.mackenzie.autumn.lang.compiler.typesystem.AbstractType
      • high.mackenzie.autumn.lang.compiler.typesystem.AbstractDeclaredType
        • high.mackenzie.autumn.lang.compiler.typesystem.ReflectiveDeclaredType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAnnotatable, IAnnotationType, IClassType, IDeclaredType, IElementType, IEnumType, IExpressionType, IInterfaceType, IReferenceType, IReturnType, IType, IVariableType

    public class ReflectiveDeclaredType
extends AbstractDeclaredType
implements IAnnotationType, IClassType, IEnumType, IInterfaceType
    An instance of this class is the type of an annotation, class, enum, or interface that was already into a java.lang.ClassLoader.
